  ('Bearded Collie', 'BEARDED COLLIE', 'bearded-collie', 1, 'Cani da pastore e bovari', 'Il Bearded Collie è una razza canina di origine britannica riconosciuta dalla FCI.', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/50/Bearded_collie_and_a_rope.jpg/330px-Bearded_collie_and_a_rope.jpg', 'Regno Unito', 'grande', false, false, 271, 'https://www.fci.be/en/nomenclature/BEARDED-COLLIE-271.html', 'Wikimedia Commons (CC BY-SA)', 20, 25, 12, 14, false, '{"energy": null, "trainability": null, "shedding": 3, "barking": 4, "good_with_children": 5, "good_with_other_dogs": 5}'::jsonb, 'https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bearded_Collie'),
